chapter.dsc: Your first day in college! Get ready to meet a lot of friends… and maybe you'll find love!
You've just arrived to the nightclub together with Carla. Get ready to meet all the characters from the story!
Time to find a job! Ready to meet the powerful and sexy Professor Ramos?
After a while in college, you've started making some enemies. What's so wrong with Jennifer?
Enjoy a weekend out with Proffessor Ramos. Or should I say daddy Ramos?
Welcome to the Palace of Love of Professor Ramos! Get ready to get tender... and you might find some of the secrets of this story!
Oh, no! Carla is in the hospital! What's happened to her!? You'll have to leave Professor Ramos' house straight away! Let's hope Carla is fine!
The big homecomining game is here. Students and faculty are wearing school colors showing their school spirit. Time to throw down and have some fun!

On your way to the party, you found Professor Ramos, who came to give you back your purse. Well, that's what he says! Did he know you'll be around James too? Also, James is going crazy jealous over Ramos! A fight is about to start.
Homecoming is around the corner, and it's time for you to decide who do you want to spend the day with! Are you ready to make your choices?
Time to make a choice! You have to decide who you want to spend the last day of the semester with. Are you ready to make the final decision?
Oh, no! Malcolm is a vampire! I knew it, I totally knew it!! I should've never taken this job… or… Maybe he's not that bad. Having a vampire as a boss… that's kind of hot too!
What a day! Your first day in Vampower was so full of new feelings. You met Miya, a business partner of Malcolm, a very intriguing character. It's time to go back home and talk to Ayana!
Back to work! After a peaceful day with Ayana, you're back at Vampower, ready for whatever comes next. Maybe it's time to get some intimate time with Malcolm…
Soren just visited your place! The most fearful vampire in the world has come for revenge… And he's threatening your life! You need to find Malcolm, and tell him about this.
You've discovered the truth behind Malcolm's purposes! He's working together with Miya, from Miracle Enterprises, to develop a new medicine for humanity. What's really behind his plans?

Soren's just visited Vampower! And she's showed you very interesting tricks. He doesn't seem like a bad guy, after all. Also, you've found that Malcolm has been glamouring some of your coworkers. Something is getting The vampire attacks keep happening in town. It's time to confront Malcolm about his true purposes. Something is wrong with him!

You've told Malcolm about what happened with Soren... Now you start getting a feeling of what's really going on between these two vampires. There's more in play than a simple revenge. They're battling to conquer the entire world!

All the cards are on the table! Malcolm has revealed his true purposes. He plans to enslave the entire human race… in exchange for a healthy, and long life. However, he's using human beings for his experiments! Will you accept that?
The ritual has concluded, and the final battle is here! The two most powerful vampires in the world are facing each other! Who will you save in your final choice?
Get ready to meet Malcolm, one of the most powerful CEO in the world. What are the hidden #I#secrets#Ie# of Vampower Enterprises?
Your first day in Vampower is over… But you sense a very weird feeling through the air! What is it that it feels so dangerous about this place?
You are the Princess of the Kingdom of Themia… However, your land has been invaded! Would you be able to escape alive before the enemies kill you?
You've escaped! Your mother, the Queen of Themia, told you to visit the Mystyc Forest. Your brother, Leo, will help you get there. Will you make it to the end?
After falling into the river, you wake up in a mysterious tribe... surrounded by beautiful and powerful women. What is this place?
You start heading to the Mystic Forest with your new crew. Haleema, the most powerful warrior of the Sapphire Claw Tribe, has joined your quest. Ready for more adventures?
Daimon has found you! He's brought a few warriors with him, and he's decided to kill your friends and take you back to the castle. Will you be able to escape?
Finally, the Mystic Forest, the place where you're supposed to find all the answers about your true identity. Why is that place so mysterious?
You've found the Serf, Guardian of the Mystic Forest... However, he's not acting like an ally. Get ready for the thougest challenge!
You passed the test in the Mystic Forest! You almost die in the attempt… However, you didn't get any answers! It's time to talk to the Guardian about your future.
The Final Battle has begun! Daimon has found the whereabouts of the Tribe, and has brought a huge army with him. Will you get to defeat him?
Daimon is dead, and you've discovered new powers after saving your land. Now it's time to understand more about yourself and start developing your new skills.
There's a new threat in the Kingdom. Both the Serf and Haleema seem to be terrified by her. Meanwhile, your power keeps growing, and it's becoming very hard to control.
The death of a Queen is always bad news. A new ruler must arise, but new threats and fight for power will come with it.

The passing of Queen Hera leaves you with big shoes to fill. With her gone and you now as queen, what will happen to the Sapphire Claws and Themia knowing the Lokian Army still lurks to destroy you all?
Your reprieve with your friends has been cut short by the sudden appearance of the Lokian general Shiva. Who will win the final battle?
The Kingdom of Themia is now yours to rule. Who will you choose to rule at your side?
Welcome to the Roman Republic! Get ready to discover the world of the gladiators! Navigate the intrigue… and maybe find true love!
You met the new gladiators. Cassius is different from the others. But you have a more urgent and pressing matter: you need to talk to your husband about what happened last night.
Your husband's behaviour is getting worrying. You grew to like Cassius and even helped him recover from his fight. An old friend will visit you today. What could be the reason behind this visit?

You want to learn more about the gladiators but realized Horatius wanted to sell the gladiators, Cassius included! Time passes and the big event the gladiators have been training for has finally arrived.
The game day saw Cassius victorious! Everything would be perfect if Horatius didn't throw an orgy in your house without you knowing… You feel like a terrible event will happen today…

chapter.chaptername: The Death Of A Loved One
chapter.dsc: Claudius surprised you with Cassius. Driven mad by what he saw, he wanted to destroy you! You had no other choice but to dispose of him. Will Horatius discover your terrible secret?
Your husband is suspicious and you are convinced he's is trying to kill you! Alba's death can't be an accident! Can you make your husband confess or can you find a proof?
You and Cassius are not safe anymore. If he tried to kill you once, he'll try again. It's time to find allies and put an end to this!
You prepared your escape with the help of your allies. Horatius got what he deserved but someone saw you! Will the escape fail? The final all or nothing battle begins. Will love conquer all?
You've been invited to take part in the most popular show on TV. Summer Love, where 9 participants will fight for… love! Will you find true love and be the winner of the show?
You've already met all the contestants in the game! Everyone but Vicky is super happy to have you. Get ready! There is a competition today!

The first competition was held. Building a raft was lots of fun and you bonded a little with the others. However, with the elimination of one of the contestants, you were abruptly reminded that Summer Love was also about surviving. But don't worry, today will be more relaxing and you'll go camping!

The camping night sure was awesome. Food, drinks and silly games in a pleasant setting made you forget about the elimination. And let's not forget you got to become more intimate with Maria! Are you relaxed enough for the drama that's awaiting you today?

What was supposed to be a perfect day at the beach ended up in a big fight and two people were expelled from Summer Love. However, today should be different with a fun - or gross? - competition coming.
You ate the grossest food ever during yesterday's competition. One of the contestants even gave up and left on its own! Let's hope you can blow some steam off today.
You had your first confessional, how exciting! But not as much as the pool party held that night! As for today, you'll have to show off your cooking skills.
In the middle of the cooking competition, your best friend was expelled for cheating! Maybe today's date will boost your spirit…

WWII has just ended, you served in the military as nurse. You decide to take a romantic getaway to clear your head. A trip to Stonehenge seems like a perfect quiet get away. When you make it to Stonehenge, the visions become more vivid.
After a strange lightning bolt hit Stonehenge, you can't find Connor. You search for him, but end meeting a man that looks exactly like Connor. He's wearing a redcoat and has a British accent

You escape with Samuel, a young man who is fighting for the revolution. He brings to a village that full of sick and injured people. You jump into action and help as many people you can with no medical supplies available.

You spend a night in jail, waiting to hear the verdict of your freedom. Samuel, informs you, that you'll be executed. You walk down death row about to meet the man who sentenced you to death before your execution.

You've earned a second chance at life. It's time to get some information and a change of clothes so you no longer stand out. It’s time to talk to the people around the village asking about Stonehenge.

Your hopes of learning about Stonehenge just went up in smoke. You're confronted by a strange woman. She tells you she has the answers you seek. You go to her home the learn the truth about what's going on.
You come face to face with Isaac, the man that looks like your husband. He wants to learn where the rebels are hiding. You're careful not to give him any information.

chapter.chaptername: All's Fair in Love and War!
chapter.dsc: You've been rescued from Isaac. You're still plagued with thoughts about how you'll get back home to your own time. Samuel, takes you to a fair, to help clear your mind. Fun is the last thing on your mind.

After a night of fun, you head back to the village with Samuel. You run into Faye, at the tavern. Surprisingly she has what you need to go back home. Do you reveal your situation to Samuel, and risk being arrested?

The last leg of the race, you're so close to going home and being with Connor again. Isaac makes a surprise appearance and hinders your plans. He's come alone and says he has a strong feeling for you. It feels like your Connor, is speaking through Isaac.
Welcome to feudal Japan! An exciting time when samurais, ninjas, geishas and many others roamed the country. Get ready for funny dialogues, adventure, and of course, sexy scenes!
You'll be sent to Edo, the capital, to save your father. Yasuke, a strong foreign samurai will defend you on your way. Who knows what dangers await you?
You survived an ambush from the weirdest ninja and stopped for the night a few kilometers from the capital. Today, you'll meet Nobugaga in his castle. Will you save your father?
Nobuo has no intention to let you or your father alone! If he can't kill him, he'll take you as a wife to serve his ambitions! Luckily, you'll meet a powerful ally that might help you.
You met Tora Hanzo, the strongest ninja alive and… Goemon's sister! You accomplished the mission she gave you so… get ready to train under her!
You trained really hard under Tora. However, Nobuo caught you infiltrating his castle! This monster has a special punishment for you… What is going to happen to you!?
Thanks to Carl, you managed to escape. Whatever happened or didn't happen between the two of you is your little secret. One thing is certain: you better hide and run to escape from Nobuo!
Ambushed by the evil Nobuo and one of his soldiers, you fell in the river. By the look of it, you're between life and death… If only you could have some time to relax!
You are now aware about your father's plans and ready to act. Who would have thought your silly dad was this amazing? The conclusion is approaching! Save the Shogun (and Japan) or die trying!
Welcome to Paris! You're discovering the most romantic city in the world for the first time! Are you ready to fall in love? Pick your love interest and explore the city of love with him or her!
You've met a wonderful and super handosme guy while you were traveling in Paris. Is it love? Or is something else?
Your love interest is giving you the best time of your life! Paris is so much fun! You've started meeting wonderful people and talking about very interesting matters. Ready for more?
The journey continues! Your last day in Paris is coming to an end, but the fun is far from over! Get ready to meet more amazing people!
The night is here! You're getting ready to try some of the most French dishes in Paris! However, a mysterious woman has something to share with you...
Your trip to Paris is coming to an end and it's time to say goodbye. You better enjoy your last moments with your love interest! What's going to happen between you two?
After a crazy party in one of the most popular nightclubs in Paris... Is time to say goodbye to France!
The morning is here... But... You overslept! Will you make it on time to catch your flight? Or you'll decide to stay in France with your love interest?
You are back at school after a long break. You meet up with your friends to catch up on current events. To your surprise, a lot has changed since your first time on campus.
Everybody has been busy making a new life for themselves. Some more excited than others. But you also learn that Ramos has been busy and you decide to pay him a visit next.

On a movie set, you find Ramos in a rant. He is upset the love scene is turning the way he wants it. After seeing you he calms down and offers to give you a tour of the studio. He wants to give his thanks for helping his book become a big success

The drama at school has been manageable, but the drama from home makes a stop. Your mom has been trying to keep the burden of the divorce off your shoulders. But it has become too much for her to handle alone. She comes by to visit and spend time with her daughter.

It’s great seeing your mom and it feels great, knowing she is feeling better. Back at school, the campus is hosting charity carnival. All your friends meet up looking to have a good time. Some heads clash, and causes some tension within the group. The day can still end on a good note.

The carnival was full of surprises, and a twist nobody saw coming. You put the carnival behind and meet your mom for lunch the next day. She sounds unexpectedly more excited than she should. I wonder what caused the change in attitude.

Carla is at the end of her rope, trying to find out who the father is for her baby. You go to friends to see if any of them can help her feel better. The fact you are always there for her gives her hope.

After seeing Steven and Eric. You and Carla are blown away from the news you get from Steven. You don’t know whether to be happy, sad, or angry. Either way, you may be faced with choosing sides among your friends.

The father has been found. But instead of finding the light at the end of the tunnel. You and your friends fall deeper inside the rabbit hole. Everyone is mad at somebody else. Who would have guessed that you’d be praying for the problems from when first came to Yorkshire?

The dirty laundry has been aired and the healing can begin. At the end of the day you are all still friends, but the cracks in the friendship are still visible. For the holidays you all decide to put your differences aside. As a sign of good faith, you all come together for one last celebration.

You and the former Summer Love contestants have been invited by Maria to stay at a remote hotel in the mountains.
Will former romances be rekindled or will new flames be lit? And what of the rumours of ghosts at the hotel...

You've reunited with everyone. The passions are clearly still there. Something will happen before long.
But also, there is something off about this place. Perhaps more will be revealed over dinner?

Jason is gone, but the rest are determined to make the most of the trip. Time to catch up with some of the gang.
But a storm is coming to The Highview Hotel... maybe Jason was right?
You saw the ghost! Or something. But Miguel is definitely gone... It's time to tell the others. Which of the group can you confide in? Which will offer you comfort... and maybe more?

After a heated debate about what to do, Melanie helped you relax back in your room.
But will the peace be short-lived? And who is that being so loud in the room next door?

The power’s out and everyone is scared. The Manager says the power switch is in the attic, but will anyone dare go turn them on?
In the darkness, secrets will be revealed. How will you react to the revelations?
Love or hate it, Vicky is gone. The power is back on, but the ghost is everywhere... Is it time to leave the haunted hotel?
The escape failed and now there are even less of you. How can you escape this ghost? Perhaps there are clues that can lead you to the truth, and maybe free from the haunted hotel.
It's just you, Maria, and Max left. Everyone else has been taken by the ghost. What will you do? Fight or fly? Who will you choose? Max or Maria?

It is time to discover the truth about Highview Hotel. An old acquaintance will reveal all…
The bigger question is…will you escape from the haunted hotel with your life?

It's finally time for your Bachelorette Party. Your fiance already had his fun, now it's your turn! You head to Las Vegas to meet a group of your nearest and dearest friends to have the party of a lifetime
You've all checked in to your penthouse suite and are now ready to party the night away. It promises to be a wild night with a trip to a strip club. Meanwhile you can't stop thinking about your ex...

The visit to the strip club ended with you being chased by mobsters. Where can the weekend go from here? Back at the casino, you decide to take in some of the famous shows. But as always, things don't go as planned....

chapter.chaptername: A Night With A Pop Star
chapter.dsc: The tiger is loose inside the casino and all chaos has descended. Can you survive long enough to have a chance encounter with your favorite pop star?

After your fantasy night with Noah Sparrow, it's time to return to reality. But that might be easier said than done. In Vegas, nothing goes to plan.”,” After not seeing each other for years, your ex saves you from being attacked by at tiger. Where do you go from here? Will you let past feelings influence your future?
After not seeing each other for years, your ex saves you from being attacked by at tiger. Where do you go from here? Will you let past feelings influence your future?
After a whirlwind evening with Diana, you don't know what to think... Don't worry, the group are going to take you shopping to help you forget your troubles...
After spoiling yourselves at the shopping mall, it's back to the casino. But who should you find there but Diana. It's time to face up to your past...
You had an intense evening with Diana, but things have just gotten more intense. Bogdan and Mike have caught you and the others. What will they do to you?
What a trip! You've survived the desert, gangsters, and even tigers! Now comes your toughest challenge yet. Deciding between your fiance and your ex...

After spending a whole day inside of the cabin, it's time to go outside to meet some new people and get some fresh air!
Today is the last night left in the camping, and you've decided to go into the city with Ethan. Time flies and it's time to say goodbye. How will your last night with him be like?

It’s great seeing your mom and it feels great, knowing she is feeling better. Back at school, the campus is hosting charity carnival. All your friends meet up looking to have a good time. Some heads clash, and causes some tension within the group. The day can still end on a good note.

The carnival was full of surprises, and a twist nobody saw coming. You put the carnival behind and meet your mom for lunch the next day. She sounds unexpectedly more excited than she should. I wonder what caused the change in attitude.

Carla is at the end of her rope, trying to find out who the father is for her baby. You go to friends to see if any of them can help her feel better. The fact you are always there for her gives her hope.

After seeing Steven and Eric. You and Carla are blown away from the news you get from Steven. You don’t know whether to be happy, sad, or angry. Either way, you may be faced with choosing sides among your friends.

The father has been found. But instead of finding the light at the end of the tunnel. You and your friends fall deeper inside the rabbit hole. Everyone is mad at somebody else. Who would have guessed that you’d be praying for the problems from when first came to Yorkshire?

The dirty laundry has been aired and the healing can begin. At the end of the day you are all still friends, but the cracks in the friendship are still visible. For the holidays you all decide to put your differences aside. As a sign of good faith, you all come together for one last celebration.
You've been invited to take part in the most popular show on TV. Summer Love, where 9 participants will fight for… love! Will you find true love and be the winner of the show?
You've already met all the contestants in the game! Everyone but Vicky is super happy to have you. Get ready! There is a competition today!

The first competition was held. Building a raft was lots of fun and you bonded a little with the others. However, with the elimination of one of the contestants, you were abruptly reminded that Summer Love was also about surviving. But don't worry, today will be more relaxing and you'll go camping!

The camping night sure was awesome. Food, drinks and silly games in a pleasant setting made you forget about the elimination. And let's not forget you got to become more intimate with Maria! Are you relaxed enough for the drama that's awaiting you today?

What was supposed to be a perfect day at the beach ended up in a big fight and two people were expelled from Summer Love. However, today should be different with a fun - or gross? - competition coming.
You ate the grossest food ever during yesterday's competition. One of the contestants even gave up and left on its own! Let's hope you can blow some steam off today.
You had your first confessional, how exciting! But not as much as the pool party held that night! As for today, you'll have to show off your cooking skills.
In the middle of the cooking competition, your best friend was expelled for cheating! Maybe today's date will boost your spirit…

The long-awaited Friday night has arrived. There are plenty of fish in the sea You go out with your friends to see what you can catch.
You met Daniel at a dive bar. He turns out to be a great guy. But is he too good to be true?
You agree to pretend to be Daniel's finace'. But what will you have to do to prove you are worthy of a prince?
You meet the queen and she was a lovely person. But you learn Daniel's real finace' will be arriving soon. How will you and Daniel prove, you two are together?
The Duchess of Winsdale and The Duke of Trost. They have both expressed an interest in you. Who will you give your heart too?

You and your friends just graduated from high school. To celebrate, they planned a week-long trip to a beach house. This might be the last time you and your friends can be together, before going your separate ways.

chapter.chaptername: I Won’t Say I Am In Love
chapter.dsc: Yesterday was a coming of age moment. A question about your sexuality that makes you question who you are as a person.
During your trip with Kirsten. You reveal that you love her. She was ready to take your friendship to a new level. But now, can you still be friends?
Your friends go to the night club. You agree to go with Blair as a date. This is the no point of return. You want answers, but will it cost you your best friend?

The club ways eventful in was you did not expect. You and Kristen make up and it looks like your friendship is safe. All the girls go back to the beach house to enjoy their time without any boys to ruin the evening.
After the passing of her Aunt Ethel, you discover that she has inherited everything. Now she’s forced to move to her aunt’s home Aldridge Edge as she tries to sort out her new windfall.
After catching a glimpse of the high life, and the handsome Scott, you can’t help but wonder if this is going to be your new life. A good meal settles nerves but doesn’t settle hearts.
What starts as a shopping trip quickly turns into a cautionary tale about the perils of flying too high in the high life.

After receiving an invite to Scott’s party, you get to see the good, bad, and ugly of the wealthiest people around. After seeing firsthand the wealth and splendor of Scott’s home, the scale of his kindness and pockets can’t be underestimated.

The papers are signed and everything is officially yours. But things don’t always go so easy as Will clashes with the new lifestyle and brings up doubt about whether it’s a good fit for the two of you.

It's finally time for your Bachelorette Party. Your fiance already had his fun, now it's your turn! You head to Las Vegas to meet a group of your nearest and dearest friends to have the party of a lifetime
You've all checked in to your penthouse suite and are now ready to party the night away. It promises to be a wild night with a trip to a strip club. Meanwhile you can't stop thinking about your ex...

The visit to the strip club ended with you being chased by mobsters. Where can the weekend go from here? Back at the casino, you decide to take in some of the famous shows. But as always, things don't go as planned....
The tiger is loose inside the casino and all chaos has descended. Can you survive long enough to have a chance encounter with your favorite pop star?

After your fantasy night with Noah Sparrow, it's time to return to reality. But that might be easier said than done. In Vegas, nothing goes to plan.”,” After not seeing each other for years, your ex saves you from being attacked by at tiger. Where do you go from here? Will you let past feelings influence your future?
After not seeing each other for years, your ex saves you from being attacked by at tiger. Where do you go from here? Will you let past feelings influence your future?
After a whirlwind evening with Diana, you don't know what to think... Don't worry, the group are going to take you shopping to help you forget your troubles...
After spoiling yourselves at the shopping mall, it's back to the casino. But who should you find there but Diana. It's time to face up to your past...
You had an intense evening with Diana, but things have just gotten more intense. Bogdan and Mike have caught you and the others. What will they do to you?
What a trip! You've survived the desert, gangsters, and even tigers! Now comes your toughest challenge yet. Deciding between your fiance and your ex...

你十分清晰的感觉到，就在你的床侧，伸手就能够着的地方，有一个人，正静静地注视着你……
你手脚并用拼命往屋里爬，那双力大出奇的手却使劲地把你从屋里拉了出去……
这个女孩，怎么感觉这么熟悉？眼睛近视，白色连衣裙，她，她不就是……
你郁闷地往里走了一步，就这一步，却让你看到了足以终生后悔的一幕。
至少她说得对，这个女人已经发现了这里发生的事情，绝对不能再留了！
下雨了...你有听到吗，谁的声音？
这样有意思吗，没有下定决心就来招惹我？
好了，让我看看是哪个不长眼的东西敢欺负我的人:)
野花？我跟他没有结婚，那我不就是那朵野花？我成小三了？
这可是你自己送上门来的，别怪我！
装什么纯啊，搞得好像你没有过男人似的
这个女人知道我的存在吗？应该不知道吧？不然，怎么能笑得那么开心呢？
那笔钱是她借的，签的也是她的名字，跟我没有任何关系
发生在1935-1949年间旧上海的命运浮沉，留洋名媛与桀骜混子杜启天、军统副官唐月新、西洋老师斋梦生的爱恨纠葛。可供玩家选择江湖线、革命线、罗曼蒂克线三条，每条故事线相互穿插影响，人物在其中身份也会发生变化
角儿的难度可不小，在上台的前一刻都可能会被剔除资格...你真的，做好准备了吗？
这好戏啊——才刚刚开场呢。
诶？诶！姐姐你别哭啊！到底怎么了？告诉小爷，爷替你削了他！
小姐，外面来了两张请帖……
我携龙鳞降世，不问来处；我与蛟龙为伴，彼此相互。山林间，江淹畔，无虑闲游几多年；逢乱世，挺身处，共肩浴血战巨蜥。护族人，袒知己。众叛亲离不惧为敌。为它，我愿！
「看来死了一个还不够是吧！」小麦看向了你，被副官的枪怼在太阳穴的你与她对上目光。
烟雾从森林深处涌动过来，拿着火把的队伍后面，鬼脸士兵转动着眼珠，抽搐蹒跚地跟着，他走过的地方一路有暗红色的粘液。
